## Tools for RDM

DECIDE utilizes specialized tools for efficient data analysis and management:
- [Prosimat](pages/mydoc/tools-prosimat.html): A tool for multi-omics analysis.
- [Cat-E](pages/mydoc/tools-cate.html): An integrated platform for data analysis.
- [Metadata Generator](pages/mydoc/metadata-generator.html): For generating standardized metadata.

